{"type": "article", "id": 25442, "title": "奶酪包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163729yxmWA6BwgthLVCR2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是莫斯科的奶酪品牌 Violette 最近更新的包装设计，他们通过调查发现消费者对于原本包装没有好感而决定更新。将 5 种口味用不同的颜色来代表，活泼鲜艳而适合女性。盖子上有四分之一的面积是食品的图案，像是时针和分针切割后的区域，更直观地说明了用法，很生活化。在包装材料上，他们用更高质量的塑料盒纸板取代原本低质量的塑料，给人安全可靠的印象。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163726NmjXCgx76QSeoI2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637279QOG1sNPcTdYXRum.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163727k2b1uK6V7qSMscNo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163728euWZsXvMG1woFiKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163728SVgAG43dc9ND5Rte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163729Ma93hEuogVPqGZdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}